      "text": "摘果",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776566477,
      "updated": 1776566477
    },
    {
      "id": "69e440cc0000000000589207",
      "text": " 果実がなりすぎるとき、良質のものを得るために、幼いうちに間引くこと。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776566477,
      "updated": 1776566564
    },
    {
      "id": "69e440cd0000000000589208",
      "text": " てきか、てっか",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776566478,
      "updated": 1776566564
    },
    {
      "id": "69e440cf000000000058920c",
      "text": "[https://kotobank.jp/word/%E6%91%98%E6%9E%9C-100771#w-2056977 摘果(テキカ)とは？ 意味や使い方 - コトバンク]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776566480,
      "updated": 1776566677
    },
    {
      "id": "69e441950000000000589216",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776566678,
      "updated": 1776566678
    },
    {
      "id": "69e440cd0000000000589209",
      "text": " 摘心、摘芯",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776566478,
      "updated": 1776566564
    },
    {
      "id": "69e440d1000000000058920d",
      "text": "  果樹などの頂芽を摘みとること。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776566482,
      "updated": 1776566571
    },
    {
      "id": "69e440fa000000000058920e",
      "text": "  てきしん",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776566522,
      "updated": 1776566571
    },
    {
      "id": "69e440fb000000000058920f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776566524,
      "updated": 1776566524
    },
    {
      "id": "69e440cd000000000058920a",
      "text": " 摘芽",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776566478,
      "updated": 1776566564
    },
    {
      "id": "69e4411d0000000000589210",
      "text": "  果樹・果菜などのむだな芽をつみとって、特定部分の生育を調節すること。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776566557,
      "updated": 1776566575
    },
    {
      "id": "69e4411e0000000000589211",
      "text": "  てきが",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776566558,
      "updated": 1776566575
